content.text: Rebel Clash throws the battlefield into chaos with daring Pokémon and audacious strategies. Featuring Fighting- and Darkness-type Pokémon, powerful attacks, and mechanics that reward aggressive play, this expansion challenges Trainers to defy expectations and strike with confidence. With striking artwork, game-changing Pokémon ex, and gameplay that sparks rebellion, Rebel Clash invites you to lead the charge and prove who dominates the fight.
